Sentencas: Metal-supported solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) are promising due to their good mechanical and thermal properties.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of Ni-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Stainless steels are often used as a supporting metal.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of Ni-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In this study, the possible use of Ni as a supporting metal was tested.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of Ni-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Ni is also a good model of supporting metal due to its lack of Cr which poisons Ni anode.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of Ni-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: YSZ electrolyte and Ni-YSZ anode were coated on a porous Ni support to fabricate Ni-supported SOFC.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of Ni-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A porous Ni support in thick-film form (t similar to 150 mu m) was prepared by the mold casting of Ni powders.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of Ni-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: An anode and an electrolyte layer were sequentially coated on the Ni support using screen printing and tape casting methods, respectively.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of Ni-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The Ni-supported cell (t similar to 200 mu m) was sintered at 1400 degrees C in a reducing atmosphere and the performance was evaluated at 800 degrees C with a La0.6Sr0.4CO0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF) cathode.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of Ni-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The unit cell showed an open circuit voltage (OCV) of 0.96 V and a peak power density of 470 mW/cm(2) at 800 degrees C. (C) 2009
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of Ni-supported solid oxide fuel cell
